These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
Food: mango, kiwi, peach, eggplant
Music-Genre: trance, gospel, soul, reggae
Pet: hamster, horse, fish, rabbit
Transport: scooter, helicopter, train, car
 1. Transport:helicopter == Music-Genre:gospel##1
 2. Food:peach == Music-Genre:soul##1
 3. Pet:hamster is on the right of Transport:car##1
 4. Pet:horse is on the right of Music-Genre:trance##1
 5. Food:kiwi is on the right of Music-Genre:gospel##1
 6. Transport:train is on the right of Transport:car##1
 7. Transport:scooter is on the left or right of Music-Genre:gospel##3
 8. Music-Genre:reggae is somewhere to the left of Music-Genre:soul##5
 9. Music-Genre:reggae is on the left or right of Music-Genre:trance##3
10. Pet:rabbit is somewhere to the right of Pet:fish##5
11. Transport:car is somewhere to the right of Food:eggplant##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | eggplant     | kiwi   | mango | peach |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | trance    | reggae   | soul    |
| Pet           | fish       | rabbit   | horse   | hamster     |
| Transport     | helicopter       | scooter | car  | train      |

