 4. Movie-Genre:western is somewhere to the right of Transport:van##5
 5. Beverage:juice is on the right of Pet:mouse##1
 6. Transport:van is on the far left or far right##3
 7. Movie-Genre:romance is between Movie-Genre:western and Beverage:mirinda##2
 8. Pet:chinchilla is somewhere to the left of Transport:tram##5
 9. Pet:mouse == Movie-Genre:western##1
10. Pet:chinchilla is somewhere to the right of Beverage:mirinda##5
11. Transport:train is on the left of Beverage:juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
