| Beverage      | mirinda       | hot-chocolate | sprite     | juice     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary      | romance       | western | musical |
| Pet           | turtle       | chinchilla    | mouse     | goat         |
| Transport     | van | airplane     | train     | tram       |

