 9. Transport:tram is on the left or right of Transport:bus##3
10. Transport:helicopter is on the right of Transport:van##1
11. Transport:tram is on the right of Beverage:lemonade##1
12. Transport:van is on the right of Job:scientist##1
13. Beverage:fanta is somewhere to the right of Movie-Genre:animation##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | cola      | sprite | fanta     |
| Job           | analyst   | scientist  | coach        | dressmaker |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | musical     | animation      | superhero   |
| Transport     | bus | tram | van          | helicopter     |

