.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
Food: avocado, cranberry, peach, papaya
Job: musician, analyst, manager, accountant
Movie-Genre: family, zombie, sports, musical
Music-Genre: trance, r&b, jazz, ambient
 1. Food:peach is somewhere to the right of Movie-Genre:zombie##5
 2. Music-Genre:ambient == Food:avocado##1
 3. Food:peach is somewhere to the left of Music-Genre:trance##5
 4. Job:musician is in an even position##4
 5. Job:analyst is on the left of Music-Genre:jazz##1
 6. Music-Genre:trance is somewhere to the right of Music-Genre:r&b##5
 7. Job:manager == Movie-Genre:musical##1
 8. Movie-Genre:musical is somewhere to the left of Job:musician##5
 9. Music-Genre:jazz is on the right of Food:avocado##1
10. Movie-Genre:musical is somewhere to the right of Food:peach##5
11. Movie-Genre:family is somewhere to the right of Food:papaya##5
12. Movie-Genre:zombie is somewhere to the left of Food:peach##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | avocado | peach  | papaya    | cranberry       |
| Job           | analyst  | accountant | manager | musician  |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | sports   | musical  | family     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient      | jazz    | r&b        | trance |

 